.Dd September 7, 2018
.Dt SCHEME 1
.Os "Causal Agency"
.
.Sh NAME
.Nm scheme
.Nd terminal color scheme
.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl acghilmtx
.Op Fl p Ar n
.
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
generates a terminal color scheme
and outputs it in a number of formats.
.
.Pp
The arguments are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl a
Output only the 16 ANSI colors.
This is the default.
.
.It Fl c
Output a C enum.
.
.It Fl g
Output a swatch PNG.
.
.It Fl h
Output HSV.
.
.It Fl i
Swap white and black.
.
.It Fl l
Output Linux console OSC sequences.
.
.It Fl m
Output a
.Xr mintty 1
theme.
Should be used with
.Fl t .
.
.It Fl p Ar n
Only output the color
.Ar n .
.
.It Fl t
Additionally output terminal
background,
foreground,
bold,
selection
and cursor
colors.
.
.It Fl x
Output hexadecimal RGB.
.El
